---
title: Cranberry-Apple Kale Salad with Parm Frico & Garlic Ciabatta
description: Step aside, side salad—this hearty kale version is the stuff of dinner dreams. We toss the tender greens with apple slices, roasted Brussels sprouts and sweet potato, chewy dried cranberries, and a creamy, tangy honey Dijon dressing. It’s all topped with Parm frico—aka deliciously crispy cheese wafers—for a hearty-yet-light-feeling dinner you’re going to want to make again and again.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/611d24e72bc551317b729e22-a2701873.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/cranberry-apple-kale-salad-611d24e72bc551317b729e22-c5023ded.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/cranberry-apple-kale-salad-611d24e72bc551317b729e22
time required: 30 minutes
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 870 kcal
  fat: 51 g
  saturated fat: 16 g
